  <summary date="2022-04-27T21:03:49Z" status="Introduced in House">National Guard and Reserve Incentive Pay Parity Act

This bill requires the military department concerned to pay members of the reserve components a special bonus or incentive pay in the same monthly amount that is paid to members in the regular component of the service for performing comparable work requiring comparable skills.</summary>
